 />\n加條撚咩, 今時今日正常人只會甩名一開二, 仲有人加名咁笨實?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e322546c98f4980802898c96f99f921e0f861c","tid":499574,"uid":129221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:52:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但我唔明層樓落名同係咪基督徒有咩關係?</blockquote><br />\n伯母唔想我做佢未來媳婦呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a54cbf835ce2aa3fa45c448ece7f50ddd4a0b4b","tid":499574,"uid":78770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:53:58.000Z","msg":"無名唔幫手供係常識啦<br />\n同埋 你接受到食飯要AA嘅 你咪繼續囉.."},{"pid":"ab1039a4b907eef7b392060f7aadaf7afb741bd2","tid":499574,"uid":129221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:56:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>結婚離婚都叫有得分，男女友就供，你傻咗？<br />\n如果你有份全，你一係當交租。一係就白食住算。</blockquote><br />\n我無份住 因為我屋企好近公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 星期六去都唔會過夜 因為佢係基督徒比較保守<br />\n我驚因爲我唔幫手供令佢唔想娶我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋我唔幫手到時供完都唔好意思叫佢落埋我名啦"},{"pid":"26feb126140a2d7e41c321725b90fd2ae7cbe3ca","tid":499574,"uid":73366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:56:55.000Z","msg":"有你名就供，無就唔供，就算佢係你老公都係咁話"},{"pid":"7d02685422cf1a8be7c5e5d2ceec8f823fc997b7","tid":499574,"uid":129221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:57:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無名唔幫手供係常識啦<br />\n同埋 你接受到食飯要AA嘅 你咪繼續囉..</blockquote><br />\n唉 都ok既 食平野姐 但係節日/紀念日慶祝想食貴啲都唔得 除非我自己出錢 旅行就可能一年都去唔到一次了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c665b61f7734aa89329d830ff00732e2a771cb0","tid":499574,"uid":129221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T04:00:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有你名就供，無就唔供，就算佢係你老公都係咁話</blockquote><br />\n我驚我唔幫手供遲早比佢呀媽搞到我地分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85cbc1d67b6759f7d3c326e3519cbe4cf129d0ff","tid":499574,"uid":161243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T04:00:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>假膠都咁多人認真覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ncase study</blockquote><br />\n呢D豬西現實世界已經絕種"},{"pid":"af5b6e5c9eb1078e487d89c4924211abf2f87734","tid":499574,"uid":70135,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T04:02:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>結婚離婚都叫有得分，男女友就供，你傻咗？<br />\n如果你有份全，你一係當交租。一係就白食住算。</blockquote><br />\n我無份住 因為我屋企好近公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 星期六去都唔會過夜 因為佢係基督徒比較保守<br />\n我驚因爲我唔幫手供令佢唔想娶我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋我唔幫手到時供完都唔好意思叫佢落埋我名啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁咪唔落名囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你結婚為左層樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ec92c6692e107afc445f09350da9bbe96c2ea4e","tid":499574,"uid":78770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T04:03:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無名唔幫手供係常識啦<br />\n同埋 你接受到食飯要AA嘅 你咪繼續囉..</blockquote><br />\n唉 都ok既 食平野姐 但係節日/紀念日慶祝想食貴啲都唔得 除非我自己出錢 旅行就可能一年都去唔到一次了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同男朋友<br />\n拍拖一開始都講明 食飯我4佢6 或者我3佢7<br />\n大家搵幾多就按比例俾返幾多<br />\n<br />\n旅行一定係佢出大我出少<br />\n唔係叫你完全唔出 但點